tactu5

Class Cluster

  • java.lang.Object
    • tactu5.Cluster
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, T5Containers

    public class Cluster
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, T5Containers
    Cluster class allows to create chord instances with Tactu5. It's possible to pass an array of Note to the constructor or to add Note objects afterwards. This class automatically clones the Note objects passed.
    Author:
    Alessandro Capozzo - www.abstract-codex.net - summer - autumn 2007, RBDGT (www.rbdgt.be)
